[
  {
    "startTime": 1.0,
    "endTime": 2.6,
    "text": "Welcome to the lesson!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.6,
    "endTime": 6.1,
    "text": "You're about to learn how to use the past perfect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.36,
    "endTime": 9.100000000000001,
    "text": "to talk about new experiences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.1,
    "endTime": 12.1,
    "text": "Remember, the past perfect is made with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.1,
    "endTime": 13.5,
    "text": "'had'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.5,
    "endTime": 14.5,
    "text": "'not'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.5,
    "endTime": 16.4,
    "text": "if it's negative"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.4,
    "endTime": 19.299,
    "text": "plus the past participle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.6,
    "endTime": 21.3,
    "text": "and with this meaning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.3,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "it's very common to use the preposition 'before'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.866,
    "endTime": 27.966,
    "text": "Have..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.966,
    "endTime": 28.966,
    "text": "you met Ben?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.766,
    "endTime": 33.166,
    "text": "A few years ago, he got his first job at a shoe store."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.766,
    "endTime": 35.666,
    "text": "As it was his first job"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.666,
    "endTime": 39.65,
    "text": "he did many things for the first time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.866,
    "endTime": 42.866,
    "text": "For example, he helped a customer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.566,
    "endTime": 45.266000000000005,
    "text": "He used a cash register"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.966,
    "endTime": 47.766,
    "text": "and he cleaned a store"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.366,
    "endTime": 51.66,
    "text": "All of these things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.66,
    "endTime": 54.666,
    "text": "were brand new experiences in his life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.666,
    "endTime": 57.766,
    "text": "Let's look at how to talk about these things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.766,
    "endTime": 59.366,
    "text": "using the past perfect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.166,
    "endTime": 62.464999999999996,
    "text": "Here is the grammatical structure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.866,
    "endTime": 64.965,
    "text": "First, you put the subject"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.766,
    "endTime": 67.96600000000001,
    "text": "Then, the verb phrase"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.966,
    "endTime": 71.64999999999999,
    "text": "Which begins with the auxiliary verb 'had'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.466,
    "endTime": 73.666,
    "text": "then the negative particle 'not'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.166,
    "endTime": 76.566,
    "text": "Actually, with this meaning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.566,
    "endTime": 79.566,
    "text": "It is more common to use never"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.566,
    "endTime": 81.266,
    "text": "instead of 'not'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.666,
    "endTime": 84.366,
    "text": "This makes your meaning stronger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.666,
    "endTime": 86.666,
    "text": "plus the past participle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.2,
    "endTime": 89.60000000000001,
    "text": "then comes the object"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 93.0,
    "text": "and finally the preposition 'before'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.6,
    "endTime": 96.6,
    "text": "However, before is optional"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.6,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "Take a look at out first example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.8,
    "endTime": 103.2,
    "text": "He used a cash register for the first time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.9,
    "endTime": 107.7,
    "text": "In our new sentence, the subject will stay the same"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.3,
    "endTime": 109.1,
    "text": "'He'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.4,
    "endTime": 112.60000000000001,
    "text": "Now the verb phrase 'had never used'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.1,
    "endTime": 114.5,
    "text": "and the object"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.0,
    "endTime": 116.3,
    "text": "'a cash register'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.7,
    "endTime": 118.7,
    "text": "and finally, 'before'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.7,
    "endTime": 120.9,
    "text": "This gives us the sentence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.9,
    "endTime": 124.2,
    "text": "He had never used a cash register before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.5,
    "endTime": 127.4,
    "text": "Now, our next example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.9,
    "endTime": 130.4,
    "text": "The verb is 'cleaned'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "He had never cleaned a store before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.9,
    "endTime": 138.9,
    "text": "And in our final example the verb is 'helped'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.8,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "This becomes, 'he had never helped a customer before'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.8,
    "endTime": 146.3,
    "text": "A few months later"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.3,
    "endTime": 148.8,
    "text": "Ben met a girl named Jen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.8,
    "endTime": 150.8,
    "text": "They ended up dating for a while"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.8,
    "endTime": 153.10000000000002,
    "text": "and finally getting married"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 158.4,
    "text": "At the wedding, they each had many new experiences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.7,
    "endTime": 162.2,
    "text": "Ben wore a tuxedo for the first time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.1,
    "endTime": 164.799,
    "text": "Jen walked down the aisle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.5,
    "endTime": 166.533,
    "text": "and...they went on a honeymoon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.5,
    "endTime": 174.3,
    "text": "Here's how we would talk about these experiences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.3,
    "endTime": 176.10000000000002,
    "text": "using the past perfect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.1,
    "endTime": 179.6,
    "text": "Ben had never worn a tuxedo before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.4,
    "endTime": 183.4,
    "text": "Jen had never walked down the aisle before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.4,
    "endTime": 187.20000000000002,
    "text": "and...they had never gone on a honeymoon before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.9,
    "endTime": 191.1,
    "text": "I have a surprise for you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.1,
    "endTime": 194.299,
    "text": "More grammar!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.8,
    "endTime": 196.60000000000002,
    "text": "Try not to get too excited"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.2,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Instead of using 'before' at the end of the phrase"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "It's common to use this structure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.6,
    "endTime": 206.1,
    "text": "'Before'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.1,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "plus a clause in the past simple"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.5,
    "endTime": 212.5,
    "text": "and then a clause in the past perfect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 214.3,
    "text": "For example"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.3,
    "endTime": 216.20000000000002,
    "text": "Before he got married"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.2,
    "endTime": 219.2,
    "text": "Ben had never worn a tuxedo"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.2,
    "endTime": 223.79899999999998,
    "text": "Before she got married, Jen had never walked down the aisle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.5,
    "endTime": 230.6,
    "text": "and finally, before Ben and Jen got married,       they had never gone on a honeymoon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.6,
    "endTime": 234.6,
    "text": "Surprise, surprise, surprise"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.1,
    "endTime": 236.6,
    "text": "A few months later,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.9,
    "endTime": 238.3,
    "text": "Jen was..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.3,
    "endTime": 239.70000000000002,
    "text": "pregnant!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.0,
    "endTime": 243.7,
    "text": "What a life changing experience!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.3,
    "endTime": 248.5,
    "text": "She had a pregnancy glow for the first time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.6,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "She lived with very little sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.5,
    "endTime": 255.4,
    "text": "and...she changed a diaper"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.899,
    "endTime": 260.2,
    "text": "Now it's time to see these new experiences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.2,
    "endTime": 262.3,
    "text": "written in the past perfect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.4,
    "endTime": 267.799,
    "text": "Before she got pregnant, Jen had never had a pregnancy glow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.9,
    "endTime": 273.9,
    "text": "Before she had a baby, Jen had never lived with very little sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.8,
    "endTime": 276.8,
    "text": "and finally,..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.8,
    "endTime": 278.6,
    "text": "before she had a baby,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.6,
    "endTime": 281.20000000000005,
    "text": "jen had never changed a diaper"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 284.6,
    "text": "It's that time again"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.6,
    "endTime": 287.20000000000005,
    "text": "time to practice what you've learned"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.2,
    "endTime": 291.0,
    "text": "What you need to do is write a sentence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.0,
    "endTime": 293.6,
    "text": "talking about the new experiences given"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.6,
    "endTime": 296.70000000000005,
    "text": "using 'before' plus the past simple"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.0,
    "endTime": 299.4,
    "text": "then a clause in the past perfect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.6,
    "endTime": 301.5,
    "text": "For example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 303.4,
    "text": "Johnny went to the zoo"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.1,
    "endTime": 305.6,
    "text": "for the first time in his life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.1,
    "endTime": 308.0,
    "text": "he saw an elephant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.0,
    "endTime": 310.2,
    "text": "this becomes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.2,
    "endTime": 312.4,
    "text": "Before Johnny went to the zoo,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.4,
    "endTime": 315.299,
    "text": "he had never seen an elephant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.2,
    "endTime": 320.2,
    "text": "Here are your questions, good luck!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.333,
    "endTime": 336.233,
    "text": "Here are your answers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.233,
    "endTime": 371.33,
    "text": "If you would like more practice"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.33,
    "endTime": 373.133,
    "text": "click on the link in the description"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.133,
    "endTime": 374.733,
    "text": "to visit my website"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.133,
    "endTime": 376.933,
    "text": "There is a printable handout there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.933,
    "endTime": 379.933,
    "text": "with more questions and answers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.933,
    "endTime": 382.933,
    "text": "Thank you for watching. Have a great day!"
  }
]